 grant from the Sandler Program for Asthma Research (to JLD).</p></div></div><div id="idm139701604917760" class="tsec sec"><h2 class="head no_bottom_margin" id="idm139701604917760title">Abbreviations</h2><div class="bk-sec"><div><table class="default-table glossary"><tbody><tr><td>IBV</td><td>avian infectious bronchitis virus</td></tr><tr><td>MHV</td><td>murine hepatitis virus</td></tr><tr><td>SARS</td><td>severe acute respiratory syndrome</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div><div id="idm139701606435120" class="tsec sec headless whole_rhythm"><!--back/fn-group--><div class="fm-sec half_rhythm small"><p class="fn sec" id="n1"><p id="__p32" class="p p-first-last">\n<strong>Conflicts of Interest.</strong> The authors have declared that no conflicts of interest exist.</p></p><div><p id="__p33" class="p p-first-last">\n<strong>Author Contributions.</strong> DW, DG, and JLD conceived and designed the experiments. DW, AU, Y-TL, MS, MH, VM, and JLD performed the experiments. DW, AU, JE, JPL, and JLD analyzed the data. DW, AU, DDE, TGK, ERM, RKW, and JLD contributed reagents/materials/analysis tools. DW and JLD wrote the paper.</p></div></div></div><div id="idm139701606220384" class="tsec sec headless whole_rhythm"><!--back/fn-group--><div class="fm-sec half_rhythm small"><p class="fn sec" id="n3"><p id="__p34" class="p p-first-last">\n<strong>Note Added in Proof</strong>&#x02003;&#x02003;The correct sequences for Primer A and Primer B are 5&#x02032;-GTTTCCCAGTCACGATANNNNNNNNN and 5&#x02032;-GTTTCCCAGTCACGATA, respectively.</p></p><p class="fn sec" id="n4"><p id="__p35" class="p p-first-last">Academic Editor: Herbert Virgin, Washington University School of Medicine</p></p></div></div><div id="idm139701599947888" class="tsec sec"><h2 class="head no_bottom_margin" id="idm139701599947888title">References</h2><div class="ref-list-sec sec" id="reference-list"><ul class="back-ref-list" style="list-style-type:decimal;"><li id="pbio.0000002-Chang1"><span class="element-citatio